  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BAStateAcceptingToStringTransformer<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>
    contains the Transformer that given a State returns a true which is "true" or false depending on whether the state is accepting or not
    BAStateInitialToStringTransformer<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>
    contains the Transformer that given a State returns a true which is "true" or false depending on whether the state is initial or not
    BATransitionToStringTransformer<LABEL extends Label,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>
    contains the Transformer that given a transition return its string representation
    HyperMetadataToTransitionTransformer<LABEL extends Label,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>,TRANSITIONFACTORY extends TransitionFactory<LABEL,TRANSITION>>
    contains the Transformer that given a transition represented through GraphMetadata returns the transition
    MetadataToBAStateTransformer<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>
    contains the Transformer that given a state represented through GraphMetadata returns the state
    MetadataToBATransformer<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>
    contains the Transformer that given the Buchi automaton represented through GraphMetadata returns the corresponding automaton
    MetadataToTransitionTransformer<LABEL extends Label,LABELFACTORY extends LabelFactory<LABEL>,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>,TRANSITIONFACTORY extends TransitionFactory<LABEL,TRANSITION>>
    contains the Transformer that given a transition represented through GraphMetadata returns the transition
